name: Mens Fragrance & Body Wash Gift Set
description: This ultimate Homme gift set by Autograph is the ideal present idea for the modern man. Freshen up with the hair and body wash and finish with a spritz of eau de toilette before heading out to your festive event. This gift comes displayed in bold packaging for an extra touch of luxe.

name: Auto Infinite 100ml
description: Update your scent collection with the energetic aroma of Autograph Infinite,a rich fragrance sure to be a new favourite. Bergamot and mandarin instantly come to the nose when first enjoying followed by a heart of spicy black pepper and finished with woody cypress and geranium making it a handsome new scent for yourself or gift for someone special.

name: Shower Gel Set
description: Treat the special man in your life to a burst of rich fragrance with this premium woodspice shower gel set. This festively packaged gift set comes with four different shower gels in a travel size featuring the classic original burgundy amber and royal blue scents. Lather it up in the morning and enjoy soft supple skin throughout the day.

name: Craft Beer Can Wash Set
description: We've packaged our Groomsmith shower gel and flannel inside a beer-can package for maximum stocking filler goodness. The flannel will magically expand in water. Everything in this kit is suitable for vegetarians. Matching Groomsmith products are available.

name: Pour Homme Eau de Toilette For Men 100ml
description: L'Occitan is a panoramic and complex fragrance for men.About the brand- L'OCCITANE offers high quality beauty products and fragrances,developed following the principles of phytotherapy and aromatherapy. The textures and fragrances are inspired by the Mediterranean lifestyle- using a L'OCCITANE product is always a moment of well-being and sensory delight. LOCCITANE follow a strict formulation charter to guarantee the best quality,the best efficiency,and an optimal pleasure of use,while respecting people and environment. Striving to use high-quality,traceable,natural ingredients,they use over 200 botanical ingredients which are carefully selected for their effectiveness and their ability to give your skin the elements it needs to be beautiful.

name: Hair & Body Wash Set
description: An ideal secret Santa gift for a friend  or a treat for yourself  this Dermot O'Leary hair and body wash set is full of luxury fragrances. Trio set includes bergamot and basil,vetiver and cedarwood,and earl grey and sandalwood scents.

name: Eau de Toilette Trio Gift Set
description: Bold and richly fragrant,this woodspice aftershave trio set makes the perfect present for the well-groomed man who likes his choice of scents. This festively packaged set features the original woodspice scent,as well as two other versions with a distinctive hint of warm amber and burgundy. The bottles are an ideal size for his travel or gym bag.

name: Trio Fragrance Gift Set
description: A mix of rich and bold notes gives these Dermot O'Leary fragrances a festive twist. The perfect gift for the special person in your life,this premium trio set includes unique combinations of bergomot and basil,vetiver and cedarwood,and earl grey and sandalwood.

name: Fragrance & Body Wash Gift Set
description: Whether you're after a Secret Santa gift or an extra stocking filler,this exclusive Autograph set is a perfect pick. Comes with the original Autograph eau de toilette spray fragrance and scented hair and body wash. Suitable for vegans.

name: Eau de Toilette Gift Set
description: A lather of this original woodspice shower gel and a quick spray or two of the signature eau de toilette leaves you ready to make a memorable impression. Ideally packaged for Christmas,this premium set is perfect as a Secret Santa gift or as an extra stocking filler for the deserving man.

name: Vetiver Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: An elegant choice of daily fragrance or a finishing touch to suave evening attire,our vetiver eau de toilette brings an air of sophistication and a rich,masculine scent to any occasion. With woody aromas of vetiver and cedarwood,black pepper gives a fiery edge for a deeply refined fragrance.

name: Noir Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: A masculine and dynamic fragrance,our Homme eau de toilette opens with a cool fusion of oriental notes that unveil a deeper eucalyptus scent. Top notes in this mens fragrance feature a blend of mandarin,grapefruit and mint,before leading into warm and spicy middle notes and a deep leathery base.

name: Bergamot Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: Our Bergamot eau de toilette features a fresh yet masculine fragrance based around the refreshing,uplifting citrus tones of bergamot. These bright tones are harmonised with an undercurrent of leafy basil and precious amber to form the perfect blend of a captivating and charming scent.

name: Earl Grey & Sandalwood Gift Set
description: For the gent that likes to keep himself in check,this earl grey and sandalwood set by Dermot O'Leary makes a great Christmas gift. Includes an eau de toilette spray and scented hair and body wash. Product is suitable for vegans.

name: Earl Grey & Sandalwood Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: A refreshing fragrance for a fresh and invigorating signature scent,our earl grey and sandalwood eau de toilette from Dermot OLeary bursts with the crisp scents of bergamot and tea for aromatic top notes,with rich sandalwood and cardamom giving a warm base.

name: Bergamot & Basil Gift Set
description: Pick up this bergamot and basil gift set by Dermot O'Leary for a loved one who likes to keep his style and grooming in check. Trio set includes a scented hair and body wash,soothing aftershave balm and the signature eau de toilette fragrance. Suitable for vegetarians.

name: Homme Noir Gift Set
description: This gift set includes an eau de toilette and hair and body wash,each with the masculine Homme Noir fragrance to leave you smelling fresh. This men's set makes an excellent present for a loved one,adding a luxurious touch to their everyday routine.

name: Atropa Belladonna Eau de Parfum 100ml
description: Decadent scent of dark cassis berries blended with flower blooms of narcissus and jasmine,on a base of rich bourbon vanilla. Every Shay & Blue treasure is beautifully gift wrapped in an elegant blue box.

name: Bergamot & Basil Post Shave Balm 75ml
description: Crafted in collaboration with Dermot OLeary,this post-shave balm has been formulated to instantly calm and hydrate the skin,all while reducing the appearance of razor bumps. This after-shave balm is made with the aromatic fragrances of bergamot and basil to leave you feeling fresh after your morning shave.

name: Wellbeing Water Fragrance 100ml
description: New LHomme menthe epitomises self-confident,modern masculinity. It contains a splash of peppermint and sage,heart notes of green lemon essence and sustained by a musky,woody bottom.

name: Cedrat LHomme After-Shave Gel Cream 75ml
description: A very masculine way to scent your skin. The zesty and aquatic notes of lhomme cologne cdrat infuse this after-shave cream-gel,to leave a fresh and invigorating scent on the skin. It helps to: - moisturize and soothe the skin after shaving,- reduce feelings of irritation and tightness caused by shaving,- invigorate the skin and protect it against environmental aggressions. Apply the after-shave cream-gel to dry skin after shaving. Its smooth,non-oily texture sinks into the skin immediately.

name: Overnight Recovery 50ml
description: After a long and tiring day,skin needs some much needed TLC,and this overnight recovery face cream from Dermot OLeary ensures it receives it. Hydrating and smoothing skin as you sleep,our night cream will let you wake up to a soft and revived complexion.

name: Pour Homme Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: An invigorating and fresh choice of men's eau de toilette,our Aqua aftershave boasts a versatile fragrance that seamlessly brings an air of sophistication to day or night. With uplifting notes of citrus,cypress and marine,musk and cedarwood provide a rich and woody base.

name: Moisturising Aftershave 100ml
description: Our moisturising aftershave is the perfect way to revive dry skin or replenish it after shaving. With a soothing and refreshing scent of woody aromas and notes of spice,this is a sophisticated aftershave that will leave skin and senses feeling indulged.

name: Pour Homme Nuit Eau De Toilette 100ml
description: Enjoy the complex fragrance of our Aqua eau de toilette. Perfect for sophisticated evening looks,the blend of bergamot and cinnamon open this mens fragrance,with a touch of pepper adding warm spice. A base of cedarwood adds earthy richness,while leather and tonka beans make for delicious final notes.

name: Aftershave 100ml
description: Feel ready for everything and anything with an energising aftershave that invigorates you. Carefully formulated to smooth,soothe,and refresh,this is the perfect finish your shaving routine. Walk out the door with a lingering scent of aromatic spicy blends,with pepper mingling with base notes of precious woods before giving way to bohemian moss and patchouli for a scent both incredibly sophisticated and endlessly charming.

name: Intense Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: An intensely rich and charismatic choice of fragrance,our Intense eau de toilette from Autograph brings an air of sophistication to any event. With a rich blend of mandarin and red apple in its top notes,leather and violet heart cords and amber notes and oak wood,a base of sweet vanilla and deep musks make this an intensely irresistible scent.

name: Gentlemen Aftershave 100ml
description: Deeply earthy and timelessly classic. This men's aftershave will soothe your skin and have you feeling your most put together and sophisticated self when you smell its vibrant,rejuvenating spicy tones that highlight a woody base aroma for a classic scent,for the truly suave gentleman.

name: Sport Eau de Toilette 100ml
description: A wonderfully refreshing scent that perfectly evokes the spirit of adventure,our sport eau de toilette is a light and zesty choice of everyday fragrance for the active yet suave modern man who wants a fragrance as charismatic as he is.

name: Black Oud Vaporisateur Natural Spray 100ml
description: Determined and profound,Black Oud enchants at the first encounter of its Citrus and burning Black Pepper chords.About the brand- From Venice,Monotheme specialises in fine fragrances with a contemporary take on traditional perfume formulas. Created by master perfumier Lorenzo Vidal,the fragrances are complex and authentically Venetian.

name: Burgundy Moisturising Aftershave 100ml
description: With a sophisticated earthy fragrance,our moisturising aftershave will help refresh and revive skin after shaving or when its in need of a touch of TLC. With rich woody scents blending with benzoin,patchouli,vetiver and moss,this aftershave will reinvigorate skin.

name: YOUTHMUD Tinglexfoliate Treatment 15g
description: Originally designed as a 10-minute professional 'facial in a jar' for behind-the-scenes use in Hollywood's Entertainment,Music,Fashion & Award industries. YOUTHMUD provides gentle resurfacing exfoliation and helps to leave skin looking smoother,brighter,and softer resulting in immediate camera-ready glowing skin. For Men & Women. Get your Youthful Sexy Glow back in just 10 minutes. YOUTHMUD for Super Sexy Super Radiant Skin.

name: Jean-Marie Farina Eau de Cologne Spray 100ml
description: With Jean-Marie Farina Eau de Cologne rediscover the fragrances and irresistible freshness of an Italian garden beside the clear waters of the Mediterranean where lemon trees and orange trees burst with sunshine.

name: L'Homme Cologne Cedrat Eau de Toilette 75ml
description: A fragrance for men full of character,the l'homme cologne cdrat eau de toilette is the essence of escape of an endless horizon. Mingling the absolute freshness of sea spray with zesty cedrat this blend of vibrant aquatic and citrus notes is set over an intriguing base of woody spices.

name: Classic Agrumi di Sicilia Eau de Cologne Unisex 100ml
description: The delicate spring freshness of orange blossom is complemented by a sprightly top note where tones of tangerine and bitter orange lead to a flowery heart of jasmine and butterbush completed by the soft scent of white musk. For him and for her - fresh a perfect morning fragrance.

name: MINIMALIST WATCH WITH SQUARE CASE AND METAL STRAP
description: Minimalist analogue watch with a square case in silver and mineral crystal. The hours are marked with lines on a black face. It has a smaller face that counts seconds. Silver metal strap. Automatic safety clasp. Links can be removed to fit it to your wrist. Water resistant (3 ATM); cannot be worn in the shower or bath nor for diving.

name: MINIMALIST WATCH WITH EMBOSSED BLACK LEATHER STRAP
description: Minimalist analogue watch with a round case in silver and mineral crystal. The hours are marked with lines on a white face. Black leather strap with animal embossing. Buckle and double loop for fastening. Water resistant up to 50 m / 19.6?etres (5 ATM); can be worn in the shower or bath but is not suitable for diving.

name: MINIMALIST WATCH WITH SQUARE CASE AND BLACK LEATHER STRAP
description: Minimalist analogue watch with a square case in silver and mineral crystal. The hours are marked with lines on a black face. It has a smaller face that counts seconds. name: MINIMALIST WATCH WITH ROUND CASE AND METAL STRAP
description: Minimalist analogue watch with a round black case in silver and mineral crystal. The hours are marked with lines on a black face. It has a smaller face indicating the day of the week in numbers and letters. Black metal strap. Automatic safety clasp. Links can be removed to fit it to your wrist. Water resistant (3 ATM); cannot be worn in the shower or bath or for diving.

Dark brown leather strap. Fastening with buckle and double loop. Water resistant up to 50 m / 19.6?etres (5 ATM); can be worn in the shower or bath but not for diving.

name: CONTRAST STRAP SPORTS WATCH
description: Sports watch with a round case in black and mineral glass. Featuring an inside face for the seconds hand. Contrast black and yellow strap with animal embossing. Buckle and double loop fastening. Water-resistant up to 30 m / 11.8?etres (3 ATM). Operates with quartz movement.

name: MINIMAL WATCH WITH BLUE LEATHER STRAP
description: Watch with a minimalist design,a round,silver-finish case and mineral glass. Dark blue leather strap. Buckle and double loop fastening. Water-resistant up to 30 m / 11.8?etres (3 ATM). Operates with quartz movement.

name: Modern Dial Watch
description: Make sure youre always on time with our mens watch,featuring a sophisticated leather strap and classic design thats sure to be noticed. A handy date display keeps you on track.

name: Bracelet Watch
description: Add the perfect finishing touch to your outfit with this metallic bracelet watch. Featuring our new linked clasp fastening. Simple round face and stick dial with a day/date window.

name: Silicone Strap Watch
description: A silicone watch is a great way to complete your outfit and this black and white one doesnt disappoint. In a stylish silicone material this watch features an adjustable strap for a comfortable fit while contrast white dials add a unique finish.

name: Casual Sub Dial Watch
description: A classic mens watch to add some style to your timekeeping the sub dial face shows each minute to the second so youll never have an excuse to be late. Perfect for everyday wear this leather strap watch secures neatly with a buckle.

name: Modern Day Watch
description: Set the finishing touch on your style with this classy modern watch. Featuring a contemporary round face and Arabic and stick dial. Faux leather strap.

name: Pure Cashmere Double Faced Scarf
description: Coordinating your winter accessories is easy with this double-faced scarf from our Autograph range. Woven from luxurious cashmere fabric for a soft,warm and lightweight feel.

name: Pure Cashmere Scarf
description: Put the finishing touch to any outfit with the sophisticated look of this luxurious cashmere scarf. Soft and plush,our mens scarf offers endless styling versatility with its solid neutral tone and fringed edging. Drape loosely around the neck on brisk weekend mornings or tie in a classic knot for the commute.

name: Pashminetta Scarf
description: Designed to be wonderfully soft,our modal rich pashminetta scarf will feel beautiful against skin,whether worn around the neck or draped over the shoulders. Finished with a fringe trim,this womens scarf is an elegant way to accessorise any look.

name: Sequin Scarf
description: Add a touch of sparkle to smart casual looks with this sequinned scarf. Striped design with scattered sequins and playful tassels at the ends.

name: Colour Block Scarf
description: It's easy to brighten up chilly days with this vibrant scarf. Long enough to wrap around for added warmth. Finished with fringing on the edges. Eye-catching colour block design.

name: Pleated Snake Print Neckerchief
description: Add a touch of vibrancy to your accessory drawer with this bold neckerchief,decorated with an on-trend snake print. Stylish pleated finish.

name: Jacquard Diamond Design Blanket Scarf
description: Wrap up warm on blustery days with this distinctive diamond design jacquard scarf. Finished with a fringed hem for a cool contemporary look.

name: Cashmere Dogstooth Scarf
description: Update your winter layers with this premium cashmere scarf. Made from a single yarn sourced from the grasslands of Inner Mongolia for a super-soft finish. Classic dogtooth print throughout,finished with a tassel hem.

name: Fair Isle Scarf
description: Boost your winter accessories collection with this eye-catching scarf. Decorated with a traditional textured Fair isle print.

name: Striped Raschel Hat & Scarf Set
description: For a smart mix-and-match look this hat and scarf set features a cool pattern and solid colour. This duo comprises a fringe-trimmed Raschel scarf featuring all-over stripes and a heathered-knit beanie with a roll-down brim for an adjustable fit.

name: Diamond Print Scarf
description: Bring a touch of sophistication to your look with this diamond print scarf. Rectangular shape with fringe detailing. The perfect complement to your business attire on a chilly day.

name: Colour Block Tassel Scarf
description: With its bold colour-flecked design,this scarf has a smart boucle look. Soft,warm style finished with tassel trims for a textural twist.

name: Pure Silk Floral Scarf
description: With its striking floral design and soft lightweight feel,this stylish scarf cocoons you in luxury. Premium silk fabric gives this springtime essential a subtle sheen.

name: Ditsy Floral Print Scarf
description: The softly romantic design of our ditsy floral scarf will bring a hint of springtime charm to your outfit. Made from recycled polyester so it's kinder to our planet.

name: Pure Silk Animal Print Scarf
description: Lightweight and lustrous,this animal print scarf will lend an elegant finish to your looks. Made from 100% silk. Designed in a long rectangular shape for easy styling.

name: Pure Silk Floral Print Scarf
description: Lend a luxurious finish to your outfits with this pure silk scarf. With a lustrous and lightweight feel,it features a painterly floral print and long rectangular shape  perfect for tying elegantly around the neck.

name: Silk Monochrome Print Skinny Scarf
description: This scarf's silky soft fabric and easy-to-pair print will lend a refined finish to your outfits. Skinny shape - perfect for tying around the neck.

name: Merino Wool Checked Scarf
description: Beat the chill in playful style by throwing on this bold checked scarf. Fringed edges add a classic touch to this winter essential. Made from soft and lightweight merino wool for a premium feel.

name: Colour Block Ribbed Scarf
description: Evoke the classic college look in this ribbed cosy scarf. Irregular blocks of colour add a bold touch.

name: Double Sided Checked Scarf
description: With a two-in-one design this scarf is easy to coordinate with your outfits. One side features a check pattern and the other a block colour. Classic rectangular shape with tassels.

name: Double Sided Checked Scarf
description: A refined herringbone check adorns this warm scarf  the perfect accessory for smart outfits. A wide shape with tasselled ends.

name: Pure Silk Leaf Print Scarf
description: Elevate simple looks with this colourful leaf print scarf. Made from pure silk for a lightweight lustrous finish. Skinny shape so you can tie it elegantly around the neck.

name: Pleated Neckerchief
description: Add a pop of colour to smart or casual outfits with this spliced spotted neckerchief. All-over pleated design for added texture.

name: Floral Pleated Scarf
description: The playful stripes and bold floral design of this scarf form a glorious splash of colour for spring. Miniature pleats add extra textural detail to this fun piece.

name: Oriental Floral Scarf
description: Lend a subtle dash of print to your looks with this floral patterned Per Una scarf. Skinny style designed to tie around the neck for a sophisticated finish.

name: Leaf Print Neckerchief
description: Add a touch of chic to your outfits with this Per Una neckerchief. Featuring a pretty leaf pattern enlivened with a pop of colour.

name: Leather Holdall
description: Keep it together in style when you're travelling with the spacious Windsor holdall. Fine-quality leather. Fitted with top handles and a detachable shoulder strap. Closes with a polished zip. Internal pockets store your essentials securely. Perfect for both business trips and weekends away.

name: Pro-Tect Oxford Cross Body Bag
description: Keep everything you need by your side in this stylish cross body bag. Durable,lightweight Pro-Tect fabric stands up to scuffs and abrasions. Features three zipped pockets to carry your things safely and neatly.

name: Leather Single Briefcase
description: Perfect for both the office and the everyday the Windsor leather briefcase carries everything you need in style. Equipped with top handles a detachable shoulder strap and zip fastenings. Internal pocket holds your laptop securely. Spacious external zip pocket makes essentials easy to access.

name: Saffiano Cross Body Bag
description: With its streamlined design and refined fabric finish our new season bag is a sophisticated way to work the cross body look. Made from a vegan-friendly Saffiano fabric. Exceptionally durable and resistance to stains.

name: Casual Leather Briefcase
description: With its trendy look and premium feel our casual briefcase is perfect for all occasions. This leather briefcase has a special storage space for your laptop and helps to keep things organised with an internal sleeve divider and zip pockets with the added convenience of a detachable shoulder strap and luggage suitcase strap.

name: Leather Messenger Bag
description: With ample space for keeping everything you need close to hand and its stylish modern look and feel this genuine leather bag is the ideal option for any occasion. It has a special laptop sleeve magnetic fastenings and zips in the pockets to give extra security. Plus this messenger bag has an adjustable strap to customise to suit you perfectly.

name: Saffiano Backpack
description: The sophisticated way to style a backpack ours is designed in a sleeker shape and a refined leather-look fabric. High-end Saffiano finish for subtle texture and exceptional durability.

name: Active Slim Backpack
description: Our slim and lightweight Active backpack is perfect for holding just a few essentials. Main compartment features useful pockets and a handy front section. Zipped side compartment handy for holding trainers or wet swimwear. Stylish and practical reflective trim.

name: Flocked Holdall
description: This stylish holdall is perfect for city breaks weekends away and business meetings. In a sophisticated flocked fabric with a detachable shoulder strap this handy bag can be worn in many ways. Featuring adjustable sides two-way zip fastening and internal compartments this holdall gives ample room to pack all your essentials.

name: Pro-Tect Scuff Resistant Bum Bag
description: Keep your personal items safe with this sleek cross body bag. A pair of zipped compartments store your cards cash and phone. Comfortable crossbody fabric strap opens with an easy-to-release pinch clip. Made from resilient durable Pro-Tect fabric it's built to handle the bumps and knocks of everyday life.

name: Leather Formal Briefcase
description: Refine your professional look with this Windsor formal leather briefcase. Fitted with a single top handle a removable shoulder strap and smart polished zip and buckle fastenings. Internal pocket holds your laptop securely. Large external zip pocket provides easy access to your essentials.

name: Scuff Resistant Pro-Tect Washbag
description: The essential washbag for the busy person it boasts two zipped compartments that open wide to allow for easy use and perfect organisation. The lightweight durable wipe-clean fabric of this Pro-Tect bag performs hard to ensure it stays looking like new while a contrast lining adds a touch of style.

name: Leather Washbag
description: Keep your toiletries neat tidy and easily accessible with the compact Windsor leather washbag. Roomy central compartment closes with a polished silver-toned zip fastening. Smart seam detail and stitching adds understated character.

name: Leather Expedition Backpack
description: Channel your inner explorer with this expedition-inspired rucksack crafted from supple premium leather. Drawstring closure for security concealed under flap. Padded adjustable straps. Handy internal pockets.

name: Leather Pocket Backpack
description: Go exploring (or commuting) in style with this spacious leather backpack. Padded adjustable straps a top handle and a large external flap pocket blend practicality with rugged style. Internal zip pocket safely stores small items.

name: Reflective Backpack
description: Stay safe and be seen at all times with this innovative reflective backpack. State-of-the art design means the fabric is illuminated by car headlights  an essential companion for cycling or walking at night. Equipped with three zipped compartments and padded adjustable straps. Large internal pocket with rip-tape fastener secures your laptop or documents.

name: Casual Leather Holdall
description: A bag for all seasons and a fantastic investment this premium leather holdall has a charming casual style with internal pockets and a secure two-zip closing. Our casual leather bag also has a strong structured bottom and feet to reduce marking and keep it looking new.

name: Active Holdall
description: With space for all your essentials this Active holdall is the ideal gym bag. Securely fastened with zips with a side compartment for storing trainers or wet swimwear. Internal zip pocket and inner shoe compartment. Choose between a sturdy detachable shoulder strap and handles. Finished with a reflective trim.

name: Pro-Tect Suit Carrier
description: Keep your suit looking fresh when you travel with our carrier. The material features our Pro-Tect technology which is durable lightweight and scuff-resistant. Two zip pockets for keeping your essentials neat. Fold-over design with a carry handle on the top and shoulder strap with padding for versatile carrying options.

name: BUMBAG
description: Featuring acid-green an LV Initials signature on black Epi leather Louis Vuittons Bumbag amps up the impact. This stylish belt bag is remarkably functional with a zip closure that keeps essentials safe.

name: BUMBAG
description: A stylish choice for the man about town the Bumbag cross-shoulder bag in supple,Monogram Eclipse canvas combines a pared-down design with numerous practical features including an adjustable strap a top handle for clutch carry and external zippered pockets for quick and secure access to belongings.

name: DAMIER COBALT RACE DISCOVERY BUMBAG
description: Crafted from new Damier Cobalt Race canvas this seasons Discovery bumbag features bright orange accents leather trim and a dynamic Louis Vuitton logo. This body-conscious adjustable belt bag can also be worn on the shoulder or slung across the chest for an on-trend look. Front and back zipped pockets keep belongings accessible and secure.

name: OUTDOOR BUMBAG
description: The Outdoor bumbag is crafted from denim fabric for a modern athletic look. Enhanced by an allover Monogram pattern this practical piece is brimming with functional details. The textile and leather strap is fully adjustable to fit perfectly around the waist while zippered compartments allow easy access to belongings. Aged gold-tone metal accents add a refined finishing touch.

name: ALPHA MESSENGER
description: Louis Vuitton ventures into outer space with the bold Alpha Messenger created for the Pre-collection Spring-Summer 2019. Crafted from dark silver Taurillon leather with utilitarian black-color hardware its signed with a rubber Louis Vuitton Paris patch. It boasts an outside pocket and two inside pockets to keep things organized and accessible.

name: AMBLER
description: Unlike other bumbags the Ambler boasts generous proportions that easily accommodate a long wallet,an iPad mini and other essentials. Superbly supple Damier Graphite adds to its appeal.

name: ANTON BRIEFCASE
description: Slim and elegant the Anton Briefcase in Damier Graphite canvas combines business-like functionality with modern masculine style. The interior accommodates a laptop and documents while the front compartment and pockets provide easy access to travel tickets passports and the like. With a removable strap for over-the-shoulder wear.

name: ARMAND BRIEFCASE
description: The Armand Briefcase is offered in Ombre calf leather a natural material appreciated by connoisseurs for its fine quality and for the rich patina it acquires with use over time. Refined detailing and flawless functionality make this sophisticated Armand model a chic practical bag for business.

name: CARTABLE
description: The new Cartable shape in gorgeous Ombr natural leather brings vintage cool to the workplace. Spacious enough for your laptop and folders. Stylish enough for any after-work social occasion.

name: CITY STEAMER XXL
description: For Summer 2019 the City Steamer XXL is made from Monogram canvas with black leather handles and strap. The largest version of this already-classic bag it features all the City Steamer signatures including the hot-stamped LV Circle Toron handles and front padlock. The zipper closure and flat inside pocket bring functionality to this luxurious travel bag.

name: MATCHPOINT BACKPACK
description: Lightweight and fashionably versatile,this sporty Matchpoint Backpackdelivers both style and comfort. It elegantly combines nylon and mesh details with Damier Coastline coated canvas for a summer-ready look.

name: MATCHPOINT HYBRID BAG
description: Tote,messenger or backpack?The Hybrid cannot be boxed in. Its perfect mix of nylon and mesh with iconic Damier Cobalt coated canvas and Taiga leather does it all with style. Lightweight and fashionably versatile,this sporty bag is a must-have.

name: MICHAEL
description: Whether for business or leisure pursuits the Michael NM is the most versatile of backpacks. Numerous pockets and compartments enhance its appeal,as indeed does its supple Damier Infini leather.

name: DISCOVERY POCHETTE
description: Stylish and sporty in Damier Infini leather the Discovery clutch is the perfect size for transporting documents and other belongings,it can be hand-carried or slipped inside a larger bag.

name: SPEEDY 40
description: For Fall-Winter 2018 Louis Vuitton revisits the iconic Speedy 40 bag in full crocodilian leather. The seasons signature Titanium hue lends a futuristic air to this sumptuous piece. Expertly crafted with luxurious detailing that includes an adjustable croco strap handles and name tag this model is finished with the subtle gleam of Titanium-colored hardware.

name: CHRISTOPHER BACKPACK PM
description: The Christopher PM conjures up the rugged spirit of a hiking pack in Monogram canvas and crocodile mat. It's equally chic at work and play and evokes a fine lifestyle.

name: PORTE-DOCUMENTS VOYAGE
description: The Porte-Documents Voyage in Monogram canvas is a modern take on Louis Vuittons iconic design. An excellent choice for the businessman,due to its lightweight feel and generous interior.

name: CHRISTOPHER OUTDOOR
description: Part of the Louis Vuitton 2054 collection the all-terrain Christopher Outdoor backpack from Virgil Abloh is made from black lambskin puffer with an embossed Monogram pattern. The hypermodern oversized dimensions and multicolor metallic LV Initials are allied with practical design elements like a functional side pocket featuring a secure inside pocket.

name: CHALK NANO BAG
description: The Chalk Nano bag showcases the distinctive Louis Vuitton Monogram pattern alongside contemporary practical details. With a supple shape inspired by climbers' chalk bags this item can be comfortably worn on the shoulder or across the body. It is decorated with a sleek chain and functional carabiner fastening on the strap which are signatures of Virgil Abloh's Spring-Summer 2019 designs.

name: CHALK SLING BAG
description: The Chalk sling bag draws inspiration from the pouches used by mountaineers to store climbing chalk. It is crafted for practicalitywith a drawstring closure providing convenient access to belongingsas well as an outside pocket for essentials. A wide shoulder strap ensures this piece is comfortable to carrywhile the allover Monogram pattern gives a stylish finish.

name: SOFT TRUNK BACKPACK PM
description: The Soft Trunk Backpack by Mens Artistic Director Virgil Abloh is fashioned from mat-black Taiga leather and signed with the rainbow X found across the collection. Fusing the suitcase with the backpack this instantly recognizable bag can be worn as a backpack or carried by hand thanks to its top handle.

name: ALPHA BACKPACK
description: Exploring the universe of space travel for the Pre-collection Spring-Summer 2019,Louis Vuitton introduces the Alpha Backpack in dark silver Taurillon leather. The traditional backpack is finished with contrasting orange lining and a rubber Louis Vuitton Paris patch. The wide opening and two outside pockets give quick access to belongings.

name: B BLOSSOM SIGNET RING,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD,ONYX AND DIAMONDS
description: From the B Blossom collection a fresh interpretation of the Monogram Flower comes this signet ring in yellow and white 18-kt gold. The iconic motif is reimagined as a stamp,composed of four sparkling diamonds set in a rounded black onyx. Hand-polished and engraved with the LV initials,it expresses a bold,modern attitude.

name: EMPREINTE BANGLE,YELLOW GOLD
description: This Empreinte bangle in 18-carat yellow gold features the trunk-nail imprints a timeless House signature. The iconic LV Initials join here the collection and serve as a clasp for this strong hinged bracelet. The Empreinte bangle can be worn stacked on the arm with other bracelets for a stylish,modern look.

name: SILVER LOCKIT COLOR BRACELET,STERLING SILVER
description: This Silver Lockit bracelet is a token of Louis Vuitton's promise to help children in urgent need. For each purchase of this bracelet,$100 will be donated on your behalf to UNICEF to help children in emergencies and in vulnerable situations around the world. A symbol of protection the engraved LV padlock is crafted from sterling silver set on a colorful adjustable cord. A cool and meaningful summer accessory it can be mixed and matched with other bracelets from the collection.

description: This Silver Lockit bracelet is a token of Louis Vuitton's promise to help children in urgent need. name: EMPREINTE BRACELET,WHITE GOLD
description: The Empreinte bracelet features the Louis Vuitton distinctive Monogram Flower motif and the trunk nails leaving their imprints around. A stylish accessory for every day,this piece shown here in 18-carat white gold can be worn on the wrist or as a pendant on a chain. Decidedly modern,it will appeal to men and women alike.

name: SILVER LOCKIT PENDANT,STERLING SILVER
description: The Silver Lockit pendant is a token of our promise to help children in urgent need. For each sale $200 will be donated on your behalf to UNICEF to help children in emergencies and in vulnerable situations around the world.

name: EMPREINTE PENDANT,WHITE GOLD
description: Inspired by nails used on historic Louis Vuitton trunks this pendant is crafted from 18-carat white-gold. The nails leave their imprints around a Monogram Flower cut-out motif which rolls playfully along its precious chain. This modern signature necklace will appeal to women and men alike.

name: B BLOSSOM MEDALLION,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD AND PAVE DIAMONDS
description: A statement jewel from the B Blossom collection this necklace is wrought from 18-kt yellow and white gold. The spherical medallion is set with the signature Monogram Flower motif composed of four diamonds surrounded by brilliant diamond pav. This adjustable piece can be worn at three different lengths either alone or layered with other Blossom jewelry.A statement jewel from the B Blossom collection this necklace is wrought from 18-kt yellow and white gold. The spherical medallion is set with the signature Monogram Flower motif composed of four diamonds surrounded by brilliant diamond pav. This adjustable piece can be worn at three different lengths either alone or layered with other Blossom jewelry.

name: EMPREINTE RING,YELLOW GOLD
description: This Empreinte ring in 18-carat yellow gold features the Louis Vuitton DNA: the iconic LV initials and the heritage trunk nail which leave their imprints. The distinctive modern design makes this signature ring a must-have jewel for Louis Vuitton lovers -- both women and men.

name: EMPREINTE PENDANT,PINK GOLD
description: Inspired by nails used on historic Louis Vuitton trunks this pendant is made from 18-carat pink gold. name: B BLOSSOM CUFF,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD AND DIAMONDS
description: From the B Blossom collection this dazzling cuff bracelet is crafted from 18-karat yellow and white gold. Five raised golden studs enrich the piece each one inlaid with a Monogram Flower motif composed of four sparkling diamonds. A bold modern jewel the bracelet features a hinged closure; the inside is engraved with the Louis Vuitton signature.

name: EMPREINTE RING,PINK GOLD
description: This Empreinte ring in 18-carat pink gold features the Louis Vuitton DNA: the iconic LV initials and the heritage trunk nail which leave their imprints. The distinctive modern design makes this signature ring a must-have jewel for Louis Vuitton lovers -- both women and men

name: EMPREINTE RING,WHITE GOLD
description: The Empreinte ring is stamped with trunk-nail imprints and bears the bold LV Initials designed by Georges Vuitton in 1896. Crafted from 18-kt white gold it is a modern substantial jewel designed to appeal to women and men alike. Offered in several sizes it is easy to wear and can be styled with other pieces for an individual look.

name: EMPREINTE BANGLE,PINK GOLD
description: This Empreinte bangle in 18-carat pink gold features the trunk-nail imprints a timeless House signature. The iconic LV Initials join here the collection and serve as a clasp for this strong hinged bracelet. The Empreinte bangle can be worn stacked on the arm with other bracelets,for a stylish,modern look.

name: B BLOSSOM MEDALLION,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD,ONYX AND DIAMONDS
description: An eye-catching jewel from the B Blossom range this medallion necklace is cast from 18kt yellow and white gold. It is strung with the collections signature motif: a Monogram Flower formed of sparkling diamonds set here within two half-spheres of polished black onyx. With its adjustable chain the pendant can be layered with other pieces for a stylish stacked effect.

name: B BLOSSOM CUFF,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD,MALACHITE AND DIAMONDS
description: Fashioned from gleaming 18-karat yellow and white gold this luxe cuff bracelet from the B Blossom line is studded with five malachite cabochons. Each rounded green stone is inlaid with four shining diamonds that form the iconic Monogram Flower motif. Fitted with a discreet hinged clasp the jewel is engraved inside with the Louis Vuitton signature.

name: B BLOSSOM SIGNET RING,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD AND PAV DIAMOND
description: This signet ring in yellow and white 18-kt gold comes from the B Blossom collection a fresh exploration of the Monogram Flower. The iconic motif is reimagined as a stamp set with sparkling diamonds and surrounded by diamond pav. Hand-polished and engraved with the LV initials this signature jewel expresses a bold modern attitude.

name: B BLOSSOM CUFF YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD AND PAV DIAMOND
description: From the B Blossom collection this sculptural bracelet in yellow and white 18-kt gold is encrusted with raised Monogram Flower motifs set with brilliant diamonds and surrounded by rich diamond pav. Hand-polished and engraved with the LV initials the cuff can be worn solo or layered with other Blossom jewels.

name: LV IDYLLE BLOSSOM PENDANT,WHITE GOLD AND DIAMONDS
description: A dazzling statement piece the LV Idylle Blossom necklace is cast from 18-kt white gold. The pendant hand-set with rich diamond pav reprises the iconic LV initials designed by Georges Vuitton in 1896 as a tribute to his father. Precious and timeless this beautifully crafted unisex jewel can be worn at three different lengths.

name: EMPREINTE PENDANT,YELLOW GOLD
description: Inspired by nails used on historic Louis Vuitton trunks this pendant is crafted from 18-carat yellow gold. The nails leave their imprints around a Monogram Flower cut-out motif which rolls playfully along its precious chain. This modern signature necklace will appeal to women and men alike.

name: EMPREINTE BRACELET,PINK GOLD
description: The Empreinte bracelet features the Louis Vuitton distinctive Monogram Flower motif and the trunk nails leaving their imprints around. A stylish accessory for every day this modern unisex piece displayed here in 18-carat pink gold can be worn on the wrist or as a pendant suspended from a chain. Definitely modern it will appeal to men and women alike.

name: B BLOSSOM SIGNET RING,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD AND DIAMONDS
description: This signet ring in yellow and white 18-kt gold comes from the B Blossom collection a fresh exploration of the Monogram Flower. The iconic motif is reimagined as a stamp composed of four sparkling diamonds. Hand-polished and engraved with the LV initials this signature jewel expresses a bold,modern attitude.

name: B BLOSSOM CUFF,YELLOW GOLD,WHITE GOLD,ONYX AND DIAMONDS
description: The B Blossom cuff in yellow and white 18-kt gold strikes a modern attitude with its black onxy cabochons each set with a Monogram Flower in shining diamonds. This hand-polished bracelet is engraved with the LV initials and fastens with a discreet clasp. Stylish on its own it can also be stacked with other Blossom pieces.

name: EMPREINTE BANGLE,WHITE GOLD
description: Cast in 18-kt white gold,the Empreinte unisex bangle features nail-head imprints,a nod to the Houses trunk-making heritage. The LV Initials motif adds a bold signature touch and also serves as a clasp for this hinged bracelet. Available in several sizes,this modern jewel can be worn solo or stacked with other pieces for an on-point look.

A cool and meaningful summer accessory,it can be mixed and matched with other bracelets from the collection.

name: Pure Silk Textured Tie

The silk is enhanced by metallic yarn,skilfully interwoven and subtly textured to catch the light. A coordinating cap can be found in the Spring-Summer 2020 Precollection.

This timeless 8 cm-wide item is produced from pure silk woven in the jacquard technique for a finish that drapes beautifully.

name: MONOGRAM FLOWER DOTS TIE
description: The Monogram Flower Dots tie brings a mixture of elegance and youthfulness to business attire. Created using a screen printing technique,it is made from pure silk for the softest touch. A House signature is provided in the form of the subtle but charming allover Monogram Flower dotted pattern.

A sophisticated Jacquard weaving technique is used to create the finely detailed pattern on pure,sumptuous silk. In a choice of five colors,it adds a nice touch of LV elegance to business or casual outfits.

A contrasted LV signature sets off the jacquard weave of this design,which coordinates with a cap from the Spring-Summer 2020 Precollection. This pure silk piece adds a luxurious finishing touch to any business outfit.

This accessory is crafted from lustrous pure silk and features a subtle LV Initials motif that adds a discreet nod to the House,created using a jacquard weave technique. This piece's elegant aesthetic can be perfectly paired with a matching pocket square.

name: MONOGRAM NEON TIE

Featuring the allover Monogram print in a reinterpreted design and rainbow colors,this item is ideal for invigorating both businesswear and casual ensembles. It is crafted from pure silk for an underlying sense of luxury.

Made from pure silk,this luxury piece is elevated through the use of the House's screen-printing technique. The classic LV Initials adorn the bottom corner for a signature finish.

description: The Dots In A Row tie is designed to brighten up business wear. It is adorned in an allover Monogram pattern,interspersed with dots for a striking effect. Woven in the jacquard technique from pure silk threads,this luxury piece is finished in a denim-effect texture for a modern vibe.

The woven silk design is meticulously crafted using a screen printing technique. An embroidered LV signature in contrasting white thread completes the sleek piece.
